# GoAngular Changelog

### v1.1.0

- The GoUsers module has been added, providing a convenient mechanism for
managing users & their data.
- GoAngular's constructor now accepts a previously joined room as an option.
This feature has been added to support applications that generate room names
after Angular's configuration stage.
- goinstant.connect has replaced goinstant.platform, GoAngular has been updated
to reflect this change, the platform provider is now the goConnect provider
though the alias will remain until Dec 15, 2013.
- A JSHint file has been added, but is not currently being used as part of the
automated deployment process.

### v1.0.2

- platformProvider now accepts a user parameter vs a token parameter.

### v1.0.1

- Resolving an error users encountered when attempting to connect using default `rooms` & `token` values.

### v1.0.0

- The beginning of time.
